* &quot;Land of the Lost&quot; characters and species
* &quot;Land of the Lost&quot; (1991 TV series), the remake of the original series
* &quot;Land of the Lost&quot; (film), a 2009 film starring Will Ferrell loosely based on the 1974 series
* &quot;Valley of the Dinosaurs&quot;, a Hanna-Barbera cartoon, also from 1974, with a somewhat similar premise

