*Cummings, E. E. &quot;Complete Poems: 1913–1962&quot;. (New York: Harcouth Brace Jovanovich, 1968). 
*Harrison, G. B. (Ed.). &quot;Shakespeare: The Complete Works&quot;. (New York: Harcourt Brace Jovanovich, 1968) 
*Hirsch, Edward. &quot;How to Read a Poem and Fall in Love with Poetry&quot;. (New York: Harcourt Brace, 1999) 
